sequenceDiagram
    participant Employer
    participant EC as EmployeeController
    participant ES as EmployeeService
    participant F as BusinessPersonFactory
    participant ER as EmployeeRepository
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    Note over Employer,DB: Workflow 1: Employer Creates New Employee

    Employer->>EC: POST /api/employees
    activate EC
    EC->>ES: createEmployee(employeeDTO)
    activate ES
    ES->>F: createEmployee(name, email, salary)
    activate F
    F-->>ES: Employee object
    deactivate F
    ES->>ES: setManager(managerId)
    ES->>ER: save(employee)
    activate ER
    ER->>DB: INSERT INTO employee
    DB-->>ER: Employee record created
    ER-->>ES: Saved employee
    deactivate ER
    ES-->>EC: EmployeeDTO
    deactivate ES
    EC-->>Employer: 201 Created
    deactivate EC